{
  "stem": "3085.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they decided to have the whole thing burned, and they had huge fires.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were supposed to-- we were recruited to do some of that work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And by that time it was winter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was cold, bitter cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And of course, we didn't have proper clothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we-- and then we had to push some of these carts that had all the belongings and all the merchandise and everything on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I remember the wheels being frozen, and we had to-- it was just an incredible task, trying to move the stuff in that winter.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And of course, we were all weakened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But even then, I mean, it just shows some of the things that you recall.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We were-- we were kids, and we had to push those carts, and it was very hard work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there was a young SS officer who was actually beating us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And there were some other SS men who were under him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I recall one or two of them, when the officer didn't look, they would pass on some sugar cubes to us, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they were SS.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You know, but-- But it just shows that human nature, no matter what, I mean, you cannot generalize.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Now, maybe these same SS killed other Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But at that point, they showed some humanity.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And when the officer didn't look, they would-- they would help us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Either because they felt it was the end anyways, and they tried to-- maybe they tried to ingratiate themselves.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I don't know why, but there were these instances where-- where some humanity was demonstrated by some of these people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And you don't forget these things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But that was the time towards the end, when-- when we were-- we had a real tough time.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
